script = ExtResource("1_r0wdv")
title = "Stacking Units"
body_text = "Units can stand on the same tile through different means (ex: [color=tomato]Fighter's Shove[/color] or [color=khaki]Protag's Throw[/color]).

Units on the same tile will all be affected by the attack/skills that target that individual tile.

This means that if you can stack two enemies on the same tile, [color=khaki]Basic Punch[/color] will hit both enemies.

